                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191201-55-off325 t18191201-55-cd326"></join>, one piece of printed cotton, containing twenty-eight yards, value 19 s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18191201-55-victim711" type="victimName">
                     John 
